name: AtomicHips
description:
AtomicHips style LORA

This LORA is focused on creation of stunning hips, tested right on Deliberate V2

  • trained on 512,768 img, normalised training set in v2 to be fully adaptative

  • work well with 0.5/0.9 weight, if you want highter weight you need to increase your res to 768 and upper or you will get artefacts

  • trained on nudes, so i recommend you to put "nude", in negative prompt or it will be hard to get clothed products

modelVersions.name: AtomicHips2
modelVersions.description:
New training from scratch, with 30 normalised entries, more adaptative to any prompt and style.
Tested right on Deliberate_V2
Network rank 8 for a damn small file
Weight between 0.5/0.9 work well, for 1 and more weights you need to up to 768 or upper res, or you will have artefacts
